---
title: One-Pot Creamy Mushroom & Leek Penne with Parmesan Cheese
description: If you have your favourite pair of slippers handy, we suggest putting them on because a bowl of creamy penne is how we’re
winding down for the day. Hum in bliss when you taste the mushrooms and leek in the sauce and with only one pot it’s a dinner
with no fuss and a whole lot of comfort.
